        "created_at": "2018-01-20T17:49:43.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>This holding was formerly part of the Domaine Vincent Girardin and is in fermage to Jean-Claude Ramonet, along with a parcel of Abbaye de Morgeot and Saint-Aubin En Remilly and Murgers des Dents du Chien. 2014 was the first vintage. I haven\u2019t actually tried it but the 2014s as a set chez Ramonet are superb. Have an article about the domaine forthcoming in the January interim issue of TWA.</p>",
