        "created_at": "2018-01-20T18:39:25.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Jerry Hey\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n Jerry Hey:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>It\u2019s not from Chartron??  I heard the Ramonet Chevalier was\u2026</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>No, that\u2019s the Clos du Cailleret in Puligny-Montrachet, this is from Chassagne.</p>\n<p>But yes, the Chevalier is.</p>",
